re%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%20He%20sold%20his%20business%20in%202014%20while%20filing%20for%20a%20divorce%2C%20and%20by%20the%20start%20of%20January%202015%2C%20he%20had%20packed%20up%20everything%20in%20New%20Mexico%20and%20moved%20to%20Costa%20Rica.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20decided%20to%20move%20after%20his%20retirement%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20learn%20Spanish%2C%20intending%20to%20move%20to%20France%20a%20few%20years%20later%20and%20learn%20French.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20discovered%20that%20neither%20my%20desire%20nor%20my%20aptitude%20was%20sufficient%20to%20allow%20me%20to%20learn%20Spanish%20in%20three%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20that%20time%2C%20I%20also%20met%20a%20woman%20who%20I%20am%20still%20involved%20with%2C%20so%20that%20nipped%20moving%20to%20France%20in%20the%20bud.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20knew%20San%20Jos%C3%A9%20would%20be%20less%20touristy%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcosta-rica-hotel-tent-suites-kasiiya-papgayo-guanacaste-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGuanacaste%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20other%20beach%20areas%2C%20though%20he%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20few%20people%20spoke%20sufficient%20English%20for%20communication.%20For%20his%20first%20year%20or%20two%2C%20while%20learning%20the%20basics%20of%20Spanish%2C%20he%20struggled%20to%20buy%20groceries%2C%20deposit%20money%20in%20the%20bank%2C%20or%20get%20around%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20started%20with%20a%20tutor%2C%20went%20to%20her%20for%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%2C%20but%20I%20realized%20that%20although%20I%20was%20learning%20a%20lot%20of%20verbs%20and%20their%20conjugations%2C%20I%20was%20still%20not%20able%20to%20understand%20a%20word%20of%20Spanish%20spoken%20by%20the%20locals%2C%26quot%3B%20Keenan%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20lucky%20enough%20to%20understand%20Spanish%20as%20a%20general%20rule%2C%20you're%20still%20going%20to%20have%20issues%20because%20they%20drop%20s