0data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261a74c8e-bc95-4848-8d87-cb1bdf7e156d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECosta%20Rica%20is%20more%20expensive%20than%20he%20thought%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKeenan%20said%20that%20when%20he%20first%20moved%20to%20Costa%20Rica%2C%20prices%20were%20cheaper%20than%20in%20the%20US%20but%20not%20by%20too%20much.%20However%2C%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-economy-recession-stock-market-crash-inflation-interest-rates-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einflation%3C%2Fa%3E%20hit%20in%20mid-2022%2C%20he%20said%20prices%20in%20his%20area%20skyrocketed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECosta%20Rica%20imposed%20import%20duties%20on%20US%20items%2C%20which%20have%20recently%20driven%20up%20prices%20for%20most%20expenses.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20US%20dollar%20has%20fallen%20by%20roughly%2025%25%20compared%20to%20the%20Costa%20Rican%20col%C3%B3n%20since%20peaking%20in%20summer%202022.%20He%20said%20prices%20when%20he%20visited%20Panama%20were%2C%20on%20the%20whole%2C%20much%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeenan%20said%20this%20is%20most%20apparent%20with%20food%20prices.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20cheapest%20cuts%20of%20beef%20at%20his%20local%20grocery%20store%20are%20roughly%20%245.50%20a%20pound.%20Steaks%2C%20many%20of%20which%20are%20imported%20from%20Argentina%2C%20come%20in%20at%20about%20%2417%20per%20pound.%20Packaged%20goods%2C%20as%20well%20as%20imported%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%2C%20are%20also%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202023%2C%20he%20bought%20a%20car%20in%20Costa%20Rica%20for%20about%20%2434%2C000%2C%20which%20the%20Kelley%20Blue%20Book%20listed%20as%20between%20%2416%2C000%20and%20%2418%2C000%20in%20the%20US.%20Though%20he%20could%20have%20shipped%20a%20car%20from%20the%20US%2C%20he%20was%20worried%20about%20all%20the%20transportation%20costs%20and%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20he%20needed%20a%20new%20car%20part%20only%20found%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20never%20bought%20a%20house%2C%20as%20he%20said%20the%20process%20can%20take%20years%20in%20Costa%20Rica.%20His%20first%20condo%20was%20about%20%241%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20while%20his%20current%20apartment%20is%20%241%2C500%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%20which%20he%20said%20was%20a%20good%20deal%20as%20he%20already%20knew%20the%20landlord.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20while%20rents%20in%20general%20are%20comparable%20to%20or%20cheaper%20than%20in%20the%20US%2C%20prices%20can%20vary%20greatly%20depending%20on%20the%20area.%20He%20estimates%20that%20prices%20have%20jumped%2050%25%20to%20100%25%20in%20some%20touristy%20areas%20along%20the%20coasts%20since%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20especially%20with%20greater%20investment%20in%20real%20estate%20from%20expats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20one%20is%20going%20to%20live%20down%20here%2C%20they%20must%20have%20close%20to%20round-the-clock%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20Keenan%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20opportunity%20for%20crime%2C%20and%20an%20unguarded%20house%20is%20a%20prime%20target%20eventually.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20recently%20left%20the%20United%20States%20for%20a%20new%20country%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ansheidlower%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ensheidlower%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-costa-rica-retirement-boomer-inflation-high-prices-priced-out-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718964121000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6671a4162efa138e03309b8a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-costa-rica-retirement-boomer-inflation-high-prices-priced-out-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gary%20Keenan%20moved%20from%20New%20Mexico%20to%20Costa%20Rica%20for%20re