rry%20Rosenfeld%20testified%20last%20week%2C%20describing%20Haspil's%20chaotic%20early%20years%20being%20raised%20in%20Brooklyn%20by%20a%20psychotic%20mother%2C%20followed%20by%20periods%20of%20foster%20care%20and%20homelessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20victim's%20sister%20shook%20her%20head%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20audience%20as%20the%20psychologist%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20finally%20gets%20himself%20into%20a%20relationship%20where%20he%20feels%20unconditional%20love%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctor%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEssentially%20he's%20terrified%20of%20the%20end%20of%20this%20relationship%20coming%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctor%20told%20jurors.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20just%20essentially%20coming%20apart%20at%20the%20seams.%20And%20the%20only%20way%20out%20is%20suicide%20or%20homicide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c5c8dc1f-b968-4e74-9c3d-0059a329f765%5C%22%3EWeeks%20of%20detailed%20planning%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECould%20it%20work%3F%20Might%20it%20convince%20even%20one%20juror%20and%20cause%20a%20mistrial%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20kind%20of%20EED%20defense%20victory%20%E2%80%94%20even%20a%20mistrial%20%E2%80%94%20would%20be%20a%20historical%20outlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York's%20extreme%20emotional%20disturbance%20defense%20and%20similar%20defenses%20in%20other%20states%20are%20almost%20always%20reserved%20for%20crimes%20of%20passion%2C%20when%20a%20homicide%20is%20committed%20by%20someone%20in%20the%20throes%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20defensible%20rage%20%E2%80%94%20upon%20finding%20one's%20spouse%20in%20bed%20with%20a%20lover%2C%20as%20one%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaspil%2C%20by%20contrast%2C%20spent%20weeks%20researching%2C%20purchasing%2C%20and%20planning%20in%20preparation%20for%20the%20killing.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EEarlier%20in%202020%2C%20Haspil%20took%20three%20trips%20to%20Saleh's%20Lagos%2C%20Nigeria%20offices%20and%20to%20his%20family's%20upstate%20New%20York%20home%20that%20he%20testified%20were%20i