also%20led%20the%20nation%20in%20new%20business%20applications%20per%20capita%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce.%20And%20the%20number%20of%20new%20business%20applications%20in%20Wyoming%20in%202022%20was%20seven%20times%20greater%20than%20in%202005%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20St.%20Louis%20Fed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Census%20Bureau%20data%2C%20Wyoming%20was%20the%20least%20populated%20state%20in%20the%20nation%20as%20of%202023%2C%20with%20584%2C057%20residents.%20Yet%2C%20Wyoming's%20population%20is%20steadily%20growing%2C%20increasing%201.2%25%20from%202020%20to%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Montana%2C%20the%20population%20increased%20by%204.5%25%20from%202020%20to%202023%2C%20according%20to%20Census%20Bureau%20data.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20yet%20another%20sign%20that%20the%20economy%20is%20heading%20away%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcities-hiring-the-most-florida-texas-california-job-growth-tech-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20coastal%20hubs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20more%20South%20and%20West.%20The%20pandemic%20shifted%20workers%20and%20money%20away%20from%20stalwarts%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-growth-housing-costs-coastal-cities-sunbelt-charleston-south-carolina-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20City%20and%20San%20Francisco%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20many%20opting%20for%20wide%20open%20(cheaper)%20spaces%20in%20areas%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-cheyenne-wyoming-real-estate-home-prices-housing-market-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWyoming%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20while%20pandemic-era%20population%20and%20job%20shifts%20may%20have%20slowed%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20business%20is%20still%20booming%20in%20Wyoming%20%E2%80%94%20perhaps%20showcasing%20a%20more%20permanent%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-to