growth%20rates%20in%20number%20of%20business%20applications%20from%202005%20to%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22acdd0575-ed86-44a5-b586-35a8792e4b7b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBusiness-friendly%20taxation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWyoming%2C%20Delaware%2C%20and%20Montana%20are%20all%20particularly%20attractive%20to%20new%20business%20owners%20due%20to%20their%20tax%20laws.%20It's%20a%20reason%20that%20entrepreneurship%20might%20stay%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWyoming%20is%20one%20of%20three%20states%20alongside%20South%20Dakota%20and%20Nevada%20that%20does%20not%20impose%20a%20corporate%20income%20tax%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftaxfoundation.org%2Fdata%2Fall%2Fstate%2Fstate-corporate-income-tax-rates-brackets-2024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETax%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Washington%20D.C.%20based%20think%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20Wyoming%20does%20not%20impose%20an%20individual%20income%20tax%2C%20another%20appeal%20for%20potential%20business%20owners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelaware%20is%20known%20for%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuilding-wilmington-delaware-largest-companies-ct-corporation-2017-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebusiness-friendly%20tax%20structure.%3C%2Fa%3E%20About%2068%25%20of%20all%20Fortune%20500%20companies%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorpfiles.delaware.gov%2FAnnual-Reports%2FDivision-of-Corporations-2022-Annual-Report-cy.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincorporated%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Delaware%20as%20of%202022%2C%20according%20to%20the%20state's%20Division%20of%20Corporations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20the%20Economic%20Innovation%20Group%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feig.org%2F2023-business-formation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20as%20of%202023%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bstartup%20surge%26quot%3B%20in%20new%20businesses%20has%20been%20led%20by%20%26quot%3Btwo%20clear%20belts%20of%20states%20in%20the%20Mountain%20West%20and%20Southeast.%26quot%3B%20For%20places%20like%20Wyoming%20and%20Delaware%2C%20EIG%20attributes%20the%20surge%20in%20applications%20partly%20to%20favorable%20state%20corporate%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20startup%20suge%20is%20both%20powered%20and%20shaped%20by%20numerous%20local%20forces%20and%20policies%20that%20will%20affect%20its%20long-term%20economic%20impact%20on%20communities%2C%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20EIG%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20small%20business%20to%20frequent%20%E2%80%94%20or%20have%20an%20idea%20you%20want%20to%20make%20a%20reality%20%E2%80%94%20you%20too%20might%20want%20to%20head%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20new%20small-business%20owner%20in%20Wyoming%2C%20Delaware%2C%20or%20Montana%3F%20Contact%20these%20reporters%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajtowfighi%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ejtowfighi%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajkaplan%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ejkaplan%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flow-tax-states-new-business-startups-wyoming-delaware-montana-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718962441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66744fa7a76074d191cd6863%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flow-tax-states-new-business-startups-wyoming-delaware-montana-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wyoming%2C%20Delaware%2C%20and%20Montana%20lead%20the%20US%20in%20new%20business%20formations%20this%20year.%20Cheap%20costs%20and%20favorable%20taxes%20are%20driving%20the%20boom.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jtowfighi%40i