ed%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20just%20hours%20before%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20set%20to%20leave%20Tihar%20jail.%20The%20agency%20The%20High%20Court%20said%20till%20it%20heard%20the%20petition%2C%20the%20trial%20court%20order%20granting%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20bail%20would%20not%20be%20acted%20upon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Solicitor%20General%20(ASG)%20SV%20Raju%2C%20representing%20the%20ED%2C%20argued%20against%20the%20trial%20court's%20decision%20to%20grant%20bail%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20labelling%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bperverse%26quot%3B%20and%20highlighting%20serious%20procedural%20irregularities.%20%26quot%3BThe%20trial%20court's%20order%20is%20completely%20flawed.%20The%20court%20said%20there%20was%20no%20direct%20proof.%20That's%20a%20wrong%20statement%20by%20the%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Raju%20said%20before%20the%20bench%20comprising%20Justices%20Sudhir%20Kumar%20Jain%20and%20Ravinder%20Dudeja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20showed%20material%20but%20nothing%20considered.%20There%20are%20two%20ways%20when%20bail%20can%20be%20cancelled.%20If%20relevant%20facts%20are%20not%20considered%20and%20irrelevant%20facts%20are%20considered%2C%20that%20is%20grounds%20for%20cancellation%20of%20bail.%20I%20am%20saying%20look%20at%20the%20soundness%20of%20the%20order.%20Could%20have%20granted%20bail%20but%20not%20in%20this%20manner.%20Totally%20perverse%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20said%20that%20the%20trial%20court%20arrived%20on%20the%20decision%20based%20on%20wrong%20facts.%20%26quot%3BOn%20wrong%20facts%2C%20wrong%20dates%2C%20you%20come%20to%20a%20conclusion%20that%20mala%20fide.%20But%20why%2C%20the%20reason%20is%20missing.%20My%20note%20not%20considered%2C%20not%20allowed%20to%20argue.%20The%20arrest%20was%20challenged.%20The%20remanding%20court%20said%20the%20arrest%20was%20correct.%20It%20was%20challenged%20before%20this%20court.%20The%20single%20judge%20said%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20the%20arrest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20a%202014%20Supreme%20Court%20precedent%2C%20Mr%20Raju%20underscored%20the%20importance%20of%20ensuring%20that%20bail%20decisions%20are%20based%20on%20sound%20legal%20reasoning%20and%20comprehensive%20evaluation%20of%20all%20pertinent%20facts.%20%26quot%3BThe%20trial%20court%20should%20not%20have%20overlooked%20relevant%20aspects%20and%20should%20not%20have%20relied%20on%20irrelevant%20considerations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20court%20did%20not%20hear%20our%20arguments%2C%20did%20not%20properly%20examine%20the%20evidence%20we%20provided%2C%20and%20dismissed%20our%20concerns%20without%20due%20consideration%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%2C%20while%20temporarily%20suspending%20the%20bail%20order%2C%20indicated%20that%20a%20thorough%20examination%20of%20the%20ED's%20petition%20would%20be%20conducted%20before%20any%20further%20decisions%20are%20made.%20%26quot%3BUntil%20the%20matter%20is%20fully%20heard%20and%20evaluated%2C%20the%20trial%20court's%20decision%20granting%20bail%20cannot%20be%20implemented%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20arrested%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20over%20money%20laundering%20allegations%20while%20framing%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20for%202021-22%2C%20which%20was%20later%20scrapped%20after%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20raised%20red%20flags.%20The%20ED%20has%20alleged%20the%20money%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20got%20from%20the%20liquor%20sellers%20was%20used%20to%20fund%20the%20party's%20campaign%20in%20Goa%20since%20he%20is%20the%20convenor%20of%20the%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718961600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ftp1ivkoo_arvind-kejriwal-jail_625x300_21_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-bail-order-cant-be-a-more-perverse-order-probe-agency-on