20here%20to%20rock%20the%20boat%20with%20%26quot%3BDownfall.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECritical%20Role%3B%20Brennan%20Lee%20Mulligan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECritical%20Role's%20new%20campaign%20arc%2C%20%26quot%3BDownfall%2C%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20helmed%20by%20%26quot%3BDimension%2020's%26quot%3B%20Brennan%20Lee%20Mulligan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20three-chapter%20series%20is%20all%20about%20the%20fall%20of%20Aeor%2C%20an%20ancient%20civilization.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20episodes%2C%20part%20of%20the%20CR%20crew's%20third%20campaign%2C%20will%20air%20on%20July%2011%2C%2018%2C%20and%2025.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20looks%20like%20%26quot%3BCritical%20Role%26quot%3B%20is%20venturing%20into%20uncharted%20nerd%20world%20territory%20again%2C%20and%20it's%20bringing%20in%20the%20big%20guns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20eight-member%20CR%20cast%20is%20on%20episode%2098%20of%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcritical-roles-campaign-3-is-peak-narrative-nostalgia-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethird%20long-running%20%26quot%3BDungeons%20%26amp%3B%20Dragons%26quot%3B%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20the%20uninitiated%2C%20this%20group%20has%20spent%20nine%20years%20creating%20everything%20from%20two%20Amazon-backed%20animated%20series%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcritical-role-unleashes-fun-chaos-daggerheart-livestream-menagerie-twitch-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboard%20games%20publishing%20arm%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCritical%20Role%26quot%3B%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20guests%20taking%20over%20for%20the%20gang's%20regular%20game%20master%2C%20Matthew%20Mercer.%20The%20crew%20is%20now%20doubling%20down%20on%20experimentation%20and%20bringing%20game%20master%20Brennan%20Lee%20Mulligan%20to%20helm%20a%20full%20campaign%20arc.%20Mulligan%20is%20the%20regular%20game%20master%20for%20%26quot%3BDimension%2020%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20tabletop%20role-playing%20game%20show%20that%20streams%20on%20Dropout%2C%20formerly%20CollegeHumor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETitled%20%26quot%3BDownfall%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20three-part%20series%20goes%20back%20in%20time%20to%20the%20fall%20of%20an%20ancient%20civilization%2C%20Aeor.%20It'll%20also%20allow%20Mulligan%20to%20flex%20his%20storytelling%20chops%2C%20perhaps%20reprising%20some%20elements%20of%20his%20first%20%26quot%3BEXU%3A%20Calamity%26quot%3B%20run%20with%20Critical%20Role%20from%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20chapters%20are%20integrated%20into%20%26quot%3BCritical%20Role's%26quot%3B%20main%20campaign%20as%20episodes%2099%20to%20101%20of%20the%20main%20storyline.%20Only%20three%20members%20of%20the%20regular%20CR%20cast%20%E2%80%94%20Laura%20Bailey%2C%20Taliesin%20Jaffe%2C%20and%20Ashley%20Johnson%20%E2%80%94%20will%20be%20playing%20in%20%26quot%3BDownfall.%26quot%3B%20They'll%20be%20joined%20by%20a%20new%20slate%20of%20guests%2C%20including%20Abubakar%20Salim%2C%20Noshir%20Dalal%2C%20and%20Nick%20Marini.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMulligan%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20own%20crew%20is%20scheduled%20to%20play%20%26quot%3BDungeons%20%26amp%3B%20Dragons%26quot%3B%20at%20a%20sold-out%20Madison%20Square%20Garden%20in%20January%20%E2%80%94%20told%20this%20writer%20in%20May%20that%20he%20was%20excited%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bdelightful%26quot%3B%20prospect%20of%20getting%20to%20work%20with%20%26quot%3BCritical%20Role%26quot%3B%20again.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Mulligan%20had%20only%20been%20billed%20as%20an%20emcee%20for%20%26quot%3BCritical%20Role's%26quot%3B%20June%20live%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20being%20overly%20sappy%20or%20sentimental%20about%20'Critical%20Role'%20and%20its%20place%20in%20the%20pantheon%20of%20actual%20play%3A%20This%20was%20like%202017%2C%20and%20I'd%20been%20working%20at%20CollegeHumor%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20Mulligan%20recalled%2C%20referencing%20%26quot%3BDimension%2020's%26quot%3B%20beginnings%20as%20a%20CollegeHumor%20s