20spared.%20A%20high-level%20committee%20is%20being%20setup%20to%20investigate%20into%20the%20matter%20of%20the%20paper%20leak%20in%20NEET-UG%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fwhat-is-ugc-net-exam-and-why-is-it-conducted-5928819%5C%22%3EUGC-NET%20exam%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA).%20Over%2030%20lakh%20candidates%20appeared%20for%20the%20two%20exams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnswering%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20NEET-UG%20would%20be%20cancelled%2C%20Mr%20Pradhan%20added%20that%20the%20government%20has%20to%20keep%20the%20interests%20of%20meritorious%20students%20as%20well.%20%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20the%20NEET%20exams%20are%20concerned%2C%20we%20are%20in%20constant%20touch%20with%20the%20Bihar%20government%20and%20the%20Patna%20Police%20will%20send%20us%20a%20detailed%20report%20soon.%20As%20per%20preliminary%20information%2C%20errors%20are%20limited%20to%20certain%20regions.%20The%20government%20has%20to%20keep%20the%20interests%20of%20meritorious%20students%20in%20mind%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20the%20various%20entrance%20exams%20held%20in%20the%20country%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fexplained-national-testing-agency-and-controversies-around-it-5930261%5C%22%3Emarred%20with%20controversies%20of%20cheating%20and%20irregularities%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20year%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam%20conducted%20by%20the%20NTA%20was%20cancelled%20based%20on%20input%20from%20federal%20cybercrime%20unit%20run%20by%20the%20Home%20Ministry.%20Investigations%20are%20meanwhile%20underway%20to%20find%20the%20paper%20leak%20in%20the%20medical%20entrance%20exam%20NEET%20UG%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedical%20entrance%20exam%20cancelled%20in%202015%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20similar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-cancels-cbse-medical-entrance-test-orders-fresh-exam-within-4-weeks-771714%5C%22%3Eexam%20failure%20took%20place%20in%202015%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20the%20undergraduate%20medical%20entrance%20exam%20previously%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcbse-re-conducts-all-india-pre-medical-test-successfully-1200555%5C%22%3EAll%20India%20Pre-Medical%20Test%20(AIPMT)%20was%20scrapped%20in%202015%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20reports%20of%20paper%20leak.%20The%20AIPMT%20was%20then%20conducted%20by%20the%20Central%20Board%20of%20Secondary%20Education%20(CBSE).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIPMT%20was%20cancelled%20after%20the%20intervention%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20exam%20was%20conducted%20on%20May%203%20across%201%2C050%20centres%20and%20was%20cancelled%20by%20the%20court%20in%20its%20June%2015%20verdict.%20The%20court%20had%20given%20CBSE%20four%20weeks%20time%20to%20re-conduct%20the%20examination%20and%20declare%20the%20result.%20It%20announced%20the%20judgement%20noting%20that%20the%20entire%20conduct%20of%20the%20AIPMT%20had%20become%20futile%20by%20a%20handful%20of%20elements%20who%20were%20trying%20to%20reap%20undue%20financial%20gain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20medical%20entrance%20exam%20was%20cancelled%20after%20investigations%20suggested%20that%20the%20question%20paper%20and%20the%20answer%20keys%20were%20circulated%20through%20electronic%20devices%20across%2010%20states.%C2%A0The%20examination%20was%20conducted%20at%201%2C065%20centres%20in%2050%20cities%20throughout%20the%20country%20and%20abroad.%C2%A0A%20total%20of%206%2C32%2C625%20candidates%20had%20registered%20for%20the%20AIPMT%20in%202015.%20Of%20these%20around%204%2C22%2C859%20candidates%20downloaded%20the%20admit%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Feducation%2Fall-you-need-to-know-about-the-aipmt-paper-leak%2Fstory-8llY4AchZVwars8FW1XvXO.html%5C%22%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20nearly%2090%20answer%20keys%20were%20electronically%20leaked%20to%20candidates%20in%20return%20for%20Rs%2015%20-20%20lakh.%20The%20Rohtak%20police%20arrested%20seven%20people%20including%20two%20doctors%20and%20an%20MBBS%20student.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20exam%20conducting%20body%20CBSE%20had%20then%20opposed%20the%20re-exam%20saying%20that%206.3%20lakh%20students%20cannot%20be%20made%20to%20take%20the%20exam%20afresh%20when%20only%2044%20students%20have%20been%20found%20involved%20in%20taking%20benefits%20through%20unfair%20means.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20responded%20saying%20that%20even%20a%20single%20entry%20through%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%20means%20would%20%26quot%3Bvitiate%26quot%3B%20the%20%26quot%3Bsanctity%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exam%20was%20later%20successfully%20conducted%20by%20the%20CBSE.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718951820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F02k74eng_exam-result-representative-_625x300_20_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fhow-paper-leak-in-2015-led-to-cancellation-of-medical-entrance-exam-5936989%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AIPMT%20was%20cancelled%20in%202015%20after%20the%20intervention%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fhow-paper-leak-in-2015-led-to-cancellation-of-medical-entrance-exam-5936989%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fhow-paper-leak-in-2015-led-to-cancellation-of-medical-entrance-exam-5936989%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fhow-paper-leak-in-2015-led-to-cancellation-of-medical-entrance-exam-5936989%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22South%20actresses%20making%20a%20mark%20in%20bollywood%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718951400000%2C%22visual%22