ion%2C%20outfit%20design%20and%20styling%2C%20and%20creative%20direction.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiagnosed%20with%20ADHD%20as%20an%20adult%2C%20Akash%20says%20he%20has%20been%20consciously%20working%20on%20himself%20through%20therapy%20and%20self-discovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20noticing%20that%20on%20some%20days%2C%20I%20could%20focus%20and%20get%20into%20the%20%E2%80%98zone%E2%80%99%20where%20nothing%20and%20no%20one%20could%20disturb%20me%20till%20I%20finished%20the%20task%20at%20hand.%20It%20could%20be%20painting%2C%20cooking%2C%20work%20or%20anything%20else.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20some%20days%20were%20really%20difficult%20where%20I%20was%20constantly%20fidgeting%20and%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20sit%20still.%20My%20mind%20would%20not%20allow%20me%20to%20write%20or%20complete%20the%20task%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Akash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20understand%20the%20reasons%20behind%20his%20struggles%20led%20to%20Akash%E2%80%99s%20ADHD%20diagnosis.%20Being%20aware%20of%20his%20mental%20health%20brought%20about%20many%20positive%20changes%2C%20shares%20the%20MasterChef%20contestant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20able%20to%20handle%20things%20better%20on%20a%20day-to-day%20basis.%20I%E2%80%99m%20able%20to%20foresee%20situations%20where%20this%20might%20affect%20my%20work%20and%20think%20of%20ways%20to%20tackle%20it.%20It%20has%20also%20helped%20me%20find%20support%20amongst%20people%20going%20through%20similar%20situations%2C%20leading%20to%20me%20treating%20myself%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20does%20he%20deal%20with%20life%20on%20days%20when%20he%20just%20can%E2%80%99t%20focus%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349834%2Ffive-tips-to-grow-fruit-trees-at-home-mango-guava-on-terrace-gardening-indian-flowers-sushma-reddy-bengaluru%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%2