ange%E2%80%99.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20low%20point%20in%20my%20life.%20I%20was%20denied%20everything%20I%20liked%2C%20even%20books%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Srivatsan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20parents%20refused%20to%20talk%20to%20him%20and%20were%20%E2%80%9Cashamed%E2%80%9D%20of%20what%20he%20had%20become%2C%20he%20adds.%20The%20only%20way%20out%2C%20they%20told%20him%2C%20was%20to%20marry%20a%20girl.%20To%20gain%20his%20parents%E2%80%99%20acceptance%20and%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20son%E2%80%9D%2C%20Srivatsan%20even%20tried%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20my%20parents%20to%20accept%20me.%20I%20went%20the%20whole%20nine%20yards%20and%20even%20saw%20a%20girl%20my%20parents%20had%20chosen.%20They%20felt%20that%20once%20I%20got%20married%20to%20a%20girl%2C%20everything%20would%20be%20okay%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20digital%20solutions%20consultant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20even%20though%20he%20wanted%20to%20make%20his%20parents%20happy%2C%20he%20realised%20that%20it%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20done%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20his%20own%20happiness.%20He%20was%20torn%20between%20being%20true%20to%20himself%20and%20submitting%20to%20his%20parent%E2%80%99s%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20trying%20his%20level%20best%20to%20conform%20to%20the%20standards%20set%20by%20society%20and%20his%20parents%2C%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20live%20a%20lie.%20At%20his%20lowest%2C%20he%20tried%20taking%20his%20own%20life.%20%E2%80%9CI%20tried%20ending%20my%20life%20to%20avoid%20bringing%20shame%20to%20the%20family.%20It%20took%20me%2048%20pills%20to%20understand%20that%20I%20too%20am%20important%20in%20this%20world.%20Dying%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20helped%20me%20understand%20about%20living.%20I%20too%20deserved%20to%20live%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20emphatically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fup