the%20couple.%20Since%20gay%20marriage%20is%20not%20legal%20in%20India%2C%20they%20had%20to%20adopt%20Sendhan%20through%20the%20Canadian%20legal%20system.%20They%20first%20brought%20Sendhan%20to%20Canada%20a%20few%20months%20before%20his%20fifth%20birthday%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20process%20was%20complicated%20because%20our%20son%20is%20an%20Indian%20citizen%20while%20I%20am%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%20and%20my%20husband%20is%20on%20his%20way%20to%20becoming%20one.%20We%20brought%20our%20son%20here%20and%20then%20started%20the%20process%20of%20adoption%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Srivatsan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20more%20than%20a%20year%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20lawyers%2C%20and%20over%2060%2C000%20Canadian%20dollars%20before%20the%20adoption%20was%20legally%20processed.%20Yet%2C%20everything%20was%20worth%20it%20as%20they%20became%20parents%20to%20a%20beautiful%2C%20inquisitive%2C%20loving%20child%2C%20they%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESeeing%20life%20in%20a%20new%20light%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20parent%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20rewarding%20experiences%2C%20shares%20Srivatsan.%20Sendhan%20came%20to%20them%20when%20he%20was%20five%20and%20took%20some%20time%20to%20adjust%20to%20the%20new%20environment.%20He%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20only%20brown%20children%20in%20a%20predominantly%20white%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri2-1718194181-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Srivatsan%20and%20Saravanan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri2-1718194181-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri2-1718194181-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-medi