e%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20brainstorming%20to%20understand%20how%20they%20can%20solve%20this%20problem%20in%20a%20scalable%20manner%2C%20they%20started%20Digital%20Paani%20in%20end%202020%2C%20piloted%20an%20IoT-enabled%20software%20that%20manages%20end-to-end%20operations%20of%20a%20water%20treatment%20plant%2C%20and%20saw%20%E2%80%9Cincredible%20results%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigital%20Paani%20is%20helping%20buildings%20and%20industries%20move%20towards%20water%20neutrality%20and%20reduce%20water%20losses%20across%20their%20campus.%20To%20do%20this%2C%20Digital%20Paani%20works%20in%20a%20stepwise%20manner%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20Maximise%20recycling%20by%20ensuring%20wastewater%20infrastructure%20is%20working%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20Helping%20industries%20and%20residential%20societies%20do%20water%20accounting%20real-time%2C%20know%20where%20they%20are%20having%20water%20losses%2C%20and%20provide%20roadmaps%20to%20reduce%20those%20losses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20Actually%20reducing%20those%20losses%20by%20providing%20operational%20excellence%20and%20management%20through%20technology%20for%20key%20assets%20contributing%20to%20water%20losses%20such%20as%20cooling%20towers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20Digital%20Paani%20is%20a%20water%20management%20platform%20that%20tracks%20and%20manages%20a%20water%20treatment%20plant%E2%80%99s%20health%20and%20performs%20tasks%20like%20equipment%20automation%2C%20providing%20WhatsApp%20updates%20to%20users%2C%20and%20guiding%20process%20management.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20offering%20real-time%20insights%2C%20complete%20control%2C%20and%2024%2F7%20management%20with%20actionable%20recommendations%2C%20they%20drive%20operational%20excellence%20for%20sustainable%20water%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Mansi%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThink%20of%20our%20platform%20as%20a%20doctor%20for%20water%20infrastructure%2C%20telling%20buildings%20what%E2%